        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">Nennyana - The sisters are pulled thus:</P><P>- go to left side of gate, jump up on wall by taking the stalagmite/rock route (that way you won't have to run through the guards at the portal)</P><P>- get one of them (they are about lvl 45 or something but have like 1k hp and cast no spells that are dangerous in the least)</P><P>- pull to Nektolous zone and kill there at ease.</P><P>Just don't try to kill one in front of the two other cause they will chainheal, and unless you have their aggro they won't run out of mana and hps.</P><P><BR><font size=-2> <b>.Vermis.Mysteriis.Defiler.Nexxus of Faith.Torvonnilous.<BR></b><BR></font><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
